'''Benny Luke''' (March 4, 1939 in [[Oakland (California)|Oakland]],<ref>{{cite web|title=Remembering Benny Luke|url=http://www.ealymaysartworks.com/news/remembrance/166-remembering-benny-luke|publisher=www.ealymaysartworks.com|accessdate=14 February 2015}}</ref> [[California]] &ndash; January 13, 2013) was an [[African American]] actor and dancer established in [[Paris]].

He is best known for playing the role of Jacob, the domestic of Renato and Albin in the trilogy of films ''[[La Cage aux Folles (film)|La Cage Aux Folles]]''. He also had a role in the film ''[[Spermula]]''.

As a dancer he mainly made his career in Parisian [[cabarets]].

He died on 13 January 2013 and was cremated at [[PÃ¨re-Lachaise]] cemetery on 17 January.<ref>[http://christophealphathifaine.blogspot.fr/2013/01/hommage-benny-luke-le-jacob-de-la-cage.html Announcement of death (in French)]</ref>

== Filmography ==
* ''[[Spermula]]'' (1976) : ''Luc''
* ''[[La Cage aux Folles (film)|La Cage Aux Folles]]'' (1978) : ''Jacob''
* ''[[La Cage aux folles 2]]'' (1980) : ''Jacob''
* ''[[La Cage aux Folles 3: The Wedding|La Cage aux folles 3]]'' (1985) : ''Jacob''

